X-WR-CALNAME:Weaver line disruption
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-09T21:45:00&endDate=2026-06-10T00:29:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWEAVER LINE: Monday 8\, Tuesday 9\, Wednesday 10 and Thursday 11 June\, after 2245 each evening\, no service between Hackney Downs and Cheshunt / Enfield Town. Use London Underground connections between Central London and Seven Sisters\, and for Rectory Road and Stoke Newington\, use Clapton station. Last trains operate at 2243 from Liverpool Street to Cheshunt (except on Wednesday when it is at 2213)\, 2250 from Enfield Town to Liverpool Street\, 2258 from Liverpool Street to Enfield Town and 2259 from Cheshunt to Liverpool Street. Replacement buses operate. PLEASE NOTE: Due to roadworks\, service L2 will not serve Theobalds Grove or Cheshunt and is revised to terminate at Waltham Cross (Lidl). This is around a 20 minute walk from Theobalds Grove and 40 minute walk from Cheshunt. For Cheshunt\, please use GREATER ANGLIA services where possible as there are no local bus services available between Waltham Cross\, Theobalds Grove and Cheshunt at the time of this closure.
DTEND:20260610T002900Z
DTSTART:20260609T214500Z
SUMMARY:Weaver line: Part Closure
UID:b3f750f2-a0a2-4504-93b0-0489ef712f0d@b3f7.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-06-07T03:30:00&endDate=2026-06-07T09:15:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nWEAVER LINE: Sunday 7 June\, until 1015\, no service between Liverpool Street and Cheshunt / Chingford / Enfield Town. Please use London Underground and London Buses connections between Liverpool Street and Hackney Downs / Seven Sisters. GREATER ANGLIA and STANSTED EXPRESS trains will not call at Hackney Downs or Seven Sisters. Replacement buses operate. PLEASE NOTE: Due to roadworks\, service L2 will not serve Theobalds Grove or Cheshunt and is revised to start and terminate at Waltham Cross (Lidl). This is around a 20 minute walk from Theobalds Grove and 40 minute walk from Cheshunt. Limited bus services operate on non-TfL routes 242 and 310 between Waltham Cross Bus Station (five minutes north of Lidl)\, Theobalds Grove Station and Cheshunt (Old Pond)\, ten minutes from the station. For Cheshunt\, please use GREATER ANGLIA services where possible.
DTEND:20260607T091500Z
DTSTART:20260607T033000Z
SUMMARY:Weaver line: Planned Closure
UID:0e72c7a7-9064-40fe-bf72-b04207620583@0e72.org
END:VEVENT
